{"tid":1792141,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"今日食了龍門冰室營養餐","createTime":"2019-12-21T11:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T19:01:38.000Z","uid":176449,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"8df6b41988c4ae1166073984e34b4305321b273a","tid":1792141,"uid":176449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d0bK0gF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd0bK0gF.png&h=342898d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聽連登仔講到好難食咁<br />\n就試下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身諗住食全日早餐但佢冇哂麥皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知連登仔平時食開咩五星級茶記<br />\n但我覺得ok幾好食<br />\n個奶油多好脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />個奶茶都幾好飲hehe<br />\n<br />\n同場加映男朋友嘅燒汁豬頸肉撈丁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Ohx9dP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Ohx9dP.png&h=aa54102b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有少少辣辣哋咁 都ok<br />\n但太多汁有啲鹹 嗌少汁會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結就係佢唔係超級好食嘅<br />\n但係正常 唔伏<br />\n我諗難食嗰啲應該係間鋪太多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋咁啱見到龍門老細<br />\n好搞笑去到邊都著西裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f70935a6b2560945a8a6474519bfa1ceeac98f","tid":1792141,"uid":176449,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:52:51.000Z","msg":"第二張係豬仔party<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64934b44c859ca21a4f10056787d487e79e3d601","tid":1792141,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"【行動po】【求推】點解1223去稅局 連登冇人講？<br />\n<a href=